---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import BlogLatestPosts from '~/components/widgets/BlogLatestPosts.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'HomeIQ — Ganzheitliche Smart Home Expertise',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>

  <section class="pt-20 pb-12 md:pt-32 md:pb-20 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 uppercase">Expertise aus Luxemburg</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-6 dark:text-white leading-[1.1]">
        Dein Zuhause, <span class="text-blue-600">einfach intelligent.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-muted mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Ich bändige die Komplexität moderner Technik. Für ein Smart Home, das unsichtbar im Hintergrund arbeitet und dir Zeit zurückgibt.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter dark:text-white">Ganzheitliche Vernetzung</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mt-4 text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Smart Home ist mehr als nur eine bunte Lampe. Wir realisieren ein Ökosystem, in dem alle Gewerke intelligent zusammenarbeiten.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-600 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-blue-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M224 56v144a16 16 0 0 1-16 16H48a16 16 0 0 1-16-16V56a16 16 0 0 1 16-16h160a16 16 0 0 1 16 16M48 56v48h160V56Zm0 144h160v-80H48Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700 font-bold text-5xl transition-colors group-hover:text-blue-100 dark:group-hover:text-slate-600">01</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Beschattung</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Intelligente Steuerung von Rollläden und Jalousien – basierend auf Sonnenstand, Außentemperatur und Präsenz.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-600 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-blue-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M200 128a72 72 0 1 1-72-72a72 72 0 0 1 72 72m40-36.8V128a112 112 0 0 1-112 112V200a72 72 0 0 0 72-72a72 72 0 0 0-72-72V16a112 112 0 0 1 112 112Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700 font-bold text-5xl transition-colors group-hover:text-blue-100 dark:group-hover:text-slate-600">02</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Klima & Luft</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Heizung, Kühlung und kontrollierte Wohnraumlüftung arbeiten Hand in Hand für das perfekte Raumklima.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-600 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-blue-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M232 128a104 104 0 1 1-104-104a104.11 104.11 0 0 1 104 104m-16 0a88 88 0 1 0-88 88a88.1 88.1 0 0 0 88-88m-60 0a28 28 0 1 1-28-28a28 28 0 0 1 28 28"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700 font-bold text-5xl transition-colors group-hover:text-blue-100 dark:group-hover:text-slate-600">03</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Beleuchtung</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">DALI, KNX oder Casambi. Professionelle Lichtszenarien – automatisiert und energieeffizient gesteuert.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-600 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-blue-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M128 40a88 88 0 1 0 88 88a88.1 88.1 0 0 0-88-88m0 160a72 72 0 1 1 72-72a72.08 72.08 0 0 1-72 72m40-72a8 8 0 0 1-8 8h-32a8 8 0 0 1-8-8V88a8 8 0 0 1 16 0v32h24a8 8 0 0 1 8 8"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700 font-bold text-5xl transition-colors group-hover:text-blue-100 dark:group-hover:text-slate-600">04</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Intelligente Sensorik</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Präsenzmelder und Luftgütesensoren sorgen automatisch für höchsten Komfort und ein gesundes Raumklima.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-600 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-blue-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M208 40H48a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v144a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h160a16 16 0 0 0 16-16V56a16 16 0 0 0-16-16m-80 144a32 32 0 1 1 32-32a32 32 0 0 1-32 32m0-48a16 16 0 1 0 16 16a16 16 0 0 0-16-16"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700 font-bold text-5xl transition-colors group-hover:text-blue-100 dark:group-hover:text-slate-600">05</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Sicherheit</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Überwachungskameras und Alarmsysteme, die intelligent mit Beleuchtung und Beschattung interagieren.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-600 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-blue-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M216 48h-40v40h40V48Zm-56 0h-40v40h40V48ZM96 48H56v40h40V48Zm120 112h-40v40h40v-40Zm-56 0h-40v40h40v-40Zm-56 0H56v40h40v-40Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700 font-bold text-5xl transition-colors group-hover:text-blue-100 dark:group-hover:text-slate-600">06</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Automatisation</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Das Gehirn deines Hauses: Komplexe Abläufe, die im Hintergrund für maximale Effizienz sorgen.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-600 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-blue-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M215.79,118.17a8,8,0,0,0-5-5.66L153.18,90.9l14.66-73.33a8,8,0,0,0-13.69-7l-112,120a8,8,0,0,0,3,13l57.63,21.61L88.16,238.43a8,8,0,0,0,13.69,7l112-120A8,8,0,0,0,215.79,118.17ZM109.37,214l10.47-52.38a8,8,0,0,0-5-9.06L62,132.71l84.62-90.66L136.16,94.43a8,8,0,0,0,5,9.06l52.8,19.8Z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700 font-bold text-5xl transition-colors group-hover:text-blue-100 dark:group-hover:text-slate-600">07</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Energiemanagement</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Vernetzung von PV, Wechselrichter und Ladestation für eine optimierte Eigenverbrauchsquote.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-600 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-blue-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M210.3 56.34l-80-24A8 8 0 0 0 120 40v128a44 44 0 1 0 16 34.65V74.12l64 19.2V152a44 44 0 1 0 16 34.65V64a8 8 0 0 0-5.7-7.66"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700 font-bold text-5xl transition-colors group-hover:text-blue-100 dark:group-hover:text-slate-600">08</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Multiroom Audio</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Lieblingsmusik in jedem Raum – nahtlos integriert über Deckenlautsprecher oder Audio-Server.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-600 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-blue-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M160 16H96a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v192a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h64a16 16 0 0 0 16-16V32a16 16 0 0 0-16-16m0 192H96V32h64zm-16-96a12 12 0 1 1-12-12a12 12 0 0 1 12 12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700 font-bold text-5xl transition-colors group-hover:text-blue-100 dark:group-hover:text-slate-600">09</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Zutrittskontrolle</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Smarte Türkommunikation und Keyless-Entry Lösungen. Sicher, protokolliert und aus der Ferne steuerbar.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter dark:text-white">Prozess & Begleitung</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mt-4 text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">Vom ersten Entwurf bis zum langfristigen Betrieb – ich bin dein fester Partner.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div class="group rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0f1115] border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 p-2 flex flex-col shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#161920] rounded-[2.2rem] p-6 flex items-center justify-between mb-6 border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="p-2 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg text-blue-500">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M200 48h-24V40a8 8 0 0 0-16 0v8H96v-8a8 8 0 0 0-16 0v8H56a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v144a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h144a16 16 0 0 0 16-16V64a16 16 0 0 0-16-16m0 160H56V80h144z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg dark:text-white uppercase tracking-widest">Planung</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="px-6 pb-8 flex-grow">
            <ul class="space-y-5">
              {[
                'Bedarfsanalyse & Beratung',
                'Elektro-Fachplanung (CAD)',
                'Herstellerauswahl & Budget',
                'Sicherheits- & Netzwerkkonzept',
                'Raumbuch Erstellung'
              ].map((item) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 group/item cursor-default">
                  <div class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500/30 group-hover/item:bg-blue-500 group-hover/item:scale-150 transition-all duration-300"></div>
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover/item:text-slate-900 dark:group-hover/item:text-white transition-colors">{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="p-4 mt-auto">
            <a href="/planung" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full py-4 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:bg-blue-600 hover:text-white transition-all font-bold text-sm shadow-sm hover:shadow-blue-500/20">
              Details zur Planung
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0f1115] border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 p-2 flex flex-col shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#161920] rounded-[2.2rem] p-6 flex items-center justify-between mb-6 border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="p-2 bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-lg text-indigo-500">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M128 24a104 104 0 1 0 104 104A104.11 104.11 0 0 0 128 24m0 192a88.1 88.1 0 0 1-88-88c0-34.42 20.48-64 50.48-77.76a88 88 0 0 1 113.28 113.28C192 191.52 162.42 212 128 212Z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg dark:text-white uppercase tracking-widest">Integration</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="px-6 pb-8 flex-grow">
            <ul class="space-y-5">
              {[
                'KNX & Matter Programmierung',
                'Schnittstellen-Konfiguration',
                'App-Setup (Apple, Google, etc.)',
                'Visualisierung & Logik',
                'Abnahme & Einweisung'
              ].map((item) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 group/item cursor-default">
                  <div class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/30 group-hover/item:bg-indigo-500 group-hover/item:scale-150 transition-all duration-300"></div>
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover/item:text-slate-900 dark:group-hover/item:text-white transition-colors">{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="p-4 mt-auto">
            <a href="/integration" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full py-4 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:bg-indigo-600 hover:text-white transition-all font-bold text-sm shadow-sm hover:shadow-indigo-500/20">
              Details zur Integration
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0f1115] border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 p-2 flex flex-col shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#161920] rounded-[2.2rem] p-6 flex items-center justify-between mb-6 border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="p-2 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-lg text-emerald-500">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M128 80a48 48 0 1 0 48 48a48.05 48.05 0 0 0-48-48m0 80a32 32 0 1 1 32-32a32 32 0 0 1-32 32m104-32a104 104 0 1 1-104-104a104.11 104.11 0 0 1 104 104m-16 0a88 88 0 1 0-88 88a88.1 88.1 0 0 0 88-88"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg dark:text-white uppercase tracking-widest">Support</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="px-6 pb-8 flex-grow">
            <ul class="space-y-5">
              {[
                'Wartung & Updates',
                'Sicherheits-Monitoring',
                'System-Optimierung',
                'Erweiterungs-Planung',
                'Remote & Vor-Ort Hilfe'
              ].map((item) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 group/item cursor-default">
                  <div class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/30 group-hover/item:bg-emerald-500 group-hover/item:scale-150 transition-all duration-300"></div>
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover/item:text-slate-900 dark:group-hover/item:text-white transition-colors">{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="p-4 mt-auto">
            <a href="/support" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full py-4 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:bg-emerald-600 hover:text-white transition-all font-bold text-sm shadow-sm hover:shadow-emerald-500/20">
              Details zum Support
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>



  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <div class="relative rounded-[2rem] md:rounded-[3.5rem] overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-blue-900 to-indigo-950 shadow-[0_35px_70px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] border border-white/10">
      
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 md:w-[600px] md:h-[600px] bg-blue-600 rounded-full opacity-[0.12] blur-[120px]"></div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between p-8 md:p-20 gap-16">
        <div class="text-white text-center lg:text-left flex-1 z-10">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md">
            <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse"></span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Ready for Smart Home?</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-[5.5rem] font-extrabold mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-none">
            Dein Projekt <br/> <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-white">startet hier.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-xl mb-12 font-light">
            Lass uns gemeinsam ein System bauen, das dich begeistert. Herstellerunabhängig, sicher und zukunftssicher.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a href="/kontakt" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl transition-all shadow-xl">
              Jetzt anfragen
            </a>
            <a href="/ueber-mich" class="border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl transition-all">
              Über mich
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 w-full lg:w-[460px]">
